  "scope_note": "Principle- and duty-level starter mapping only. GDPR Article 5 sets seven processing principles, with further duties across the regulation (DPIA Art. 35, breach notification Art. 33-34, data-subject rights Art. 15-22). CPRA/CCPA grants California consumers parallel (not identical) rights. This is privacy-program guidance, not legal advice; confirm lawful basis, scope, and rights handling with qualified counsel/DPO. SicarioSpec evidence supports a privacy program; it is not a compliance attestation.",
